attachments.title: Exclusive: Prosecutor in 'Serial' Case Goes on the Record - The Intercept
attachments.text: It was “pretty much a run-of-the-mill domestic violence murder,” prosecutor Kevin Urick said in an exclusive interview with The Intercept. By this, he means, Adnan Syed murdered Hae Min Lee in 1999.
